And that's what it is,

00:26:03.417 --> 00:26:06.083
you become a person identified with truth.

00:26:06.458 --> 00:26:07.792
You are not afraid of anyone,

00:26:08.208 --> 00:26:11.917
you always tell the truth and will tell with great power.

00:26:11.917 --> 00:26:14.792
Like you had a great poet like William Blake,

00:26:15.500 --> 00:26:17.375
who has said about these modern times

00:26:17.750 --> 00:26:20.166
that at this time the men of God –

00:26:20.542 --> 00:26:22.458
means the people who are seeking God or

00:26:22.834 --> 00:26:27.208
