Like an enlightened light can enlighten another light

00:26:41.166 --> 00:26:42.083
which is not enlightened,

00:26:42.625 --> 00:26:43.834
and then that enlightened light

00:26:44.291 --> 00:26:45.625
enlighten many other lights.

00:26:46.000 --> 00:26:47.000
Is simple as that.

00:26:47.417 --> 00:26:49.500
There’s nothing to take or give, it's just a catalyst,

00:26:49.875 --> 00:26:53.458
that you enlighten another light and that person

00:26:53.750 --> 00:26:55.000
enlightens another light.

