And this is your property, it's your own,

00:29:00.458 --> 00:29:01.959
you should know it.

00:29:02.291 --> 00:29:04.959
That's what is My humble request to all of you.

00:29:05.166 --> 00:29:08.375
May God bless you. Thank you very much.

