00:29:36.291 --> 00:29:39.959
Nada Brahma. Is this meditation compatible with Sahaja Yoga?

00:29:40.417 --> 00:29:43.500
Not at all. Not at all.

00:29:43.917 --> 00:29:46.458
You see, this Nada Brahma is, what is the benefit one

00:29:46.834 --> 00:29:51.792
gets is that you go on humming and humming like that,

00:29:52.208 --> 00:29:53.333
and a day will come

00:29:53.792 --> 00:29:55.458
when your head will be humming all the time.

00:29:56.417 --> 00:29:58.375
Now I'll tell you the reason for that, it's like this.

00:29:58.959 --> 00:30:04.250
Supposing we say anything, like we start saying “Aum” or

00:30:04.750 --> 00:30:08.375
“Hum” or anything, we do not become.

00:30:08.875 --> 00:30:11.999
Supposing I say “I am the governor of this place” –

00:30:12.333 --> 00:30:16.375
do I become? If I say I am “Aum” – do I become?

00:30:16.667 --> 00:30:19.792
By saying thing, can we become something?

00:30:20.083 --> 00:30:22.291
If we profess something, do we become?

00:30:22.667 --> 00:30:25.458
Something has to happen within.

00:30:25.834 --> 00:30:29.000
Unless and until that happens, it has no meaning, it's all

00:30:29.333 --> 00:30:30.542
outside.

00:30:30.875 --> 00:30:31.959
You can say anything.

00:30:32.250 --> 00:30:34.250
Somebody can say I have some benefits because I have

00:30:34.500 --> 00:30:36.417
been saying prayers.

00:30:36.792 --> 00:30:37.792
That's not the thing.

00:30:38.208 --> 00:30:40.417
It’s a complete transformation that you must have.

00:30:40.792 --> 00:30:42.917
And these are very dangerous things, very, very

00:30:43.291 --> 00:30:46.125
dangerous; because in the Tibet now, for example,

00:30:46.458 --> 00:30:50.709
Lama himself is a mess, I tell you, he's a big mess.

