00:31:22.250 --> 00:31:25.000
from these Tibetans who were poor people.

00:31:25.291 --> 00:31:26.000
They are so poor:

00:31:26.375 --> 00:31:28.542
they have no clothes, nothing to cover themselves.

00:31:28.999 --> 00:31:30.667
I don't say Communism is a very good thing,

00:31:31.000 --> 00:31:34.625
but what I say, that these people really exploited them.

00:31:34.917 --> 00:31:38.750
The whole of that Lhasa exhibition was such an eye-opener.

00:31:39.083 --> 00:31:44.667
Oh God! These people have looted these poor peopple,

00:31:45.166 --> 00:31:47.291
and how much they have suffered.

00:31:47.583 --> 00:31:49.999
If you go and see now Tibet, you’ll be amazed.

00:31:50.208 --> 00:31:52.542
The people don't know, they are so confused.

00:31:52.542 --> 00:31:55.291
They don't understand. They have given everything

00:31:55.709 --> 00:31:57.917
that they had to this Mr. Lama.

00:31:58.458 --> 00:32:02.291
He's touring now everywhere; no one knows what is he up to.

00:32:02.625 --> 00:32:04.792
What benefit can they give?

00:32:05.375 --> 00:32:06.583
It's a myth.

00:32:06.959 --> 00:32:08.875
The best benefit is that you become a master.

00:32:09.166 --> 00:32:10.125
You know each and everything.

00:32:10.542 --> 00:32:12.291
You know what is Kundalini, you know how to give

00:32:12.583 --> 00:32:15.333
realization other, and everything you must do.

00:32:15.750 --> 00:32:16.750
That’s the main thing.

00:32:16.999 --> 00:32:19.125
In the beginning, you do feel nice with anything,

00:32:19.417 --> 00:32:21.500
even with a drink.

00:32:21.750 --> 00:32:23.083
For the time being, in the same way,

00:32:23.500 --> 00:32:25.667
if you are humming somebody's name you might get

00:32:25.917 --> 00:32:27.917
possessed for a while and you may feel all right.

00:32:28.208 --> 00:32:29.959
Like T.M. has the same problem.

00:32:30.291 --> 00:32:32.834
T.M. people do some mantras: for the time being they feel

00:32:33.083 --> 00:32:35.458
relaxed because somebody else comes into your mind,

00:32:35.709 --> 00:32:38.709
he takes over and he starts managing your show.

00:32:38.999 --> 00:32:40.375
And when he starts managing your show, you feel

00:32:40.625 --> 00:32:41.542
relaxed.

00:32:41.834 --> 00:32:43.417
But relaxation is not the thing.

00:32:43.709 --> 00:32:45.667
You do not become a master.

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:49.667
That's the point is: when you become one with the whole,

00:32:49.959 --> 00:32:52.458
then you are relaxed because nothing is exhausted.

00:32:52.750 --> 00:32:54.041
All the time you are relaxed.

00:32:54.291 --> 00:32:57.000
But see these lamas how they look, all wrinkled, you

00:32:57.250 --> 00:32:59.375
know, you can count their wrinkles one by one.

00:32:59.375 --> 00:33:00.709
Horrible people.

00:33:00.709 --> 00:33:03.875
You cannot say that they have anything great about them.

00:33:04.125 --> 00:33:05.458
And what good have they done?

00:33:05.458 --> 00:33:07.959
I haven't seen any lama doing any good to anyone.

00:33:08.166 --> 00:33:11.792
I had a chance of sitting next to this Dalai Lama once in a

00:33:12.125 --> 00:33:15.542
dinner party when My husband was with the Prime Minister

00:33:15.959 --> 00:33:19.291
and he was called, and because the Prime MInister

00:33:19.625 --> 00:33:22.625
and because the Prime Minister’s wife would not sit,

00:33:22.959 --> 00:33:25.333
so I was sitting next to him, and I felt so hot.

00:33:25.709 --> 00:33:27.333
And the Prime Minister was Lal Bahadur Shastri and

00:33:27.792 --> 00:33:31.333
he just could – he knew all about it, about Me and he said,

00:33:31.583 --> 00:33:32.792
"Are You feeling very hot with him?"

00:33:33.083 --> 00:33:34.291
because he was a realized soul himself.

00:33:34.709 --> 00:33:36.208
I said, “Yes, terrible.”  he said, “All right,

00:33:36.458 --> 00:33:39.083
then put the another foreign minister in between."

00:33:39.375 --> 00:33:40.500
He made Me sit on the other side

00:33:40.792 --> 00:33:42.125
and the foreign minister sat there.

00:33:42.583 --> 00:33:44.000
Till you are realized you will not know.

00:33:44.333 --> 00:33:46.375
And also I must tell you, when you go to these people

00:33:46.709 --> 00:33:49.667
it's difficult for you to get realization – that also is there;

00:33:49.999 --> 00:33:51.959
because they create a problem within you.

00:33:52.166 --> 00:33:55.500
With any effort you go onto sympathetic nervous system.

00:33:55.500 --> 00:33:58.291
Any effort, as I told you, you go to sympathetic nervous

00:33:58.542 --> 00:34:00.583
system, so your sympathetic gets activated.

00:34:00.583 --> 00:34:02.166
When your sympathetic gets activated,

00:34:02.625 --> 00:34:04.583
you either move to the left or to the right.

00:34:04.875 --> 00:34:05.834
When you move to the left,

00:34:06.125 --> 00:34:07.583
you go to the collective subconscious.

00:34:07.583 --> 00:34:10.041
That is the place which is all dead within us

00:34:10.333 --> 00:34:11.583
since our creation.

00:34:11.875 --> 00:34:14.458
And cancer, as I told you yesterday, is caused by the

00:34:14.750 --> 00:34:16.500
entities from that area.

00:34:16.917 --> 00:34:19.500
And if you go to the right side – most of these lamas put

00:34:19.750 --> 00:34:20.542
you on the right.

00:34:21.041 --> 00:34:23.750
Do you know, Hitler was guided by Lama?

00:34:24.000 --> 00:34:25.917
Dalai Lama was his guru.

00:34:26.500 --> 00:34:30.041
He taught him how to capture the minds of people and put

00:34:30.333 --> 00:34:32.041
them onto this kind of a thing.

00:34:32.458 --> 00:34:35.208
It's a well-known fact. It was Dalai Lama was his guru.

00:34:35.458 --> 00:34:36.999
All these lamas are like that.

00:34:37.291 --> 00:34:38.417
But when you are realized,

00:34:38.709 --> 00:34:40.208
then only you will know what they are.

00:34:40.583 --> 00:34:43.999
Like My grand-daughter is, was about five years –

00:34:44.250 --> 00:34:46.917
she's a realized soul; while My daughter and son-in-law

00:34:46.917 --> 00:34:48.291
were not realized souls.

00:34:48.709 --> 00:34:51.333
And once they went to Ladakh and the lama was sitting,

00:34:51.625 --> 00:34:53.333
you see, on a mount.

00:34:53.333 --> 00:34:55.041
And everybody was going and bowing to him,

00:34:55.375 --> 00:34:56.333
but she didn't like it.

00:34:56.750 --> 00:34:59.458
And when the parents went and bowed to him

00:34:59.458 --> 00:35:01.667
she got very angry – she was only five years.

00:35:01.667 --> 00:35:04.083
She just put back her hands like this, stood before him.

00:35:04.500 --> 00:35:06.125
She said, “By wearing this maxi,

00:35:06.417 --> 00:35:08.125
do you think you have become a realized soul?

00:35:08.500 --> 00:35:11.333
You are not. You have no business to ask people to bow

00:35:11.834 --> 00:35:13.709
to ask people to bow before you. What business have you got?"

00:35:13.999 --> 00:35:15.125
And they were so shocked and embarrassed,

00:35:15.458 --> 00:35:16.208
they said, “Don’t say like … ”

00:35:16.458 --> 00:35:19.667
“No, why did you bow to him? He's not to be bowed.”

00:35:20.000 --> 00:35:21.000
Just imagine!

00:35:21.375 --> 00:35:22.917
But unless and until you are realized …

00:35:23.208 --> 00:35:25.625
Also it's very difficult, because they have a very nice

00:35:25.959 --> 00:35:31.583
business propositions, they have very nice advertising

00:35:31.834 --> 00:35:33.375
agencies.

00:35:33.750 --> 00:35:35.667
Like the other day I went to Spain, I was shocked.

00:35:35.959 --> 00:35:38.375
There's another thing these lamas have started, that we

00:35:38.375 --> 00:35:42.083
have to go to Gobi Desert, Gobi Desert. Now imagine!

00:35:42.417 --> 00:35:44.875
That Gobi Desert is a place where you go for even one

00:35:45.083 --> 00:35:46.333
mile, you'll be finished.

00:35:46.750 --> 00:35:48.709
For nirvana you go to Gobi Desert.

00:35:49.041 --> 00:35:50.959
So take all the money from the people now, they prepare

00:35:51.250 --> 00:35:54.417
nicely and take crowds of people to Gobi Desert.

00:35:54.667 --> 00:35:57.000
Poor things are walking towards their death –

00:35:57.333 --> 00:35:59.125
and they call “it’s a nirvana.” They never return.

00:35:59.500 --> 00:36:01.999
So they have gone to their nirvana, they are not returned.

00:36:02.291 --> 00:36:04.083
This is how they are working it out.

00:36:04.417 --> 00:36:06.083
I've had people in England –

00:36:06.333 --> 00:36:07.542
there was one fellow called Omkar.

00:36:07.917 --> 00:36:09.458
His name was given as Omkar by some –

00:36:09.959 --> 00:36:11.959
I don't know what lama gave him that name,

00:36:12.208 --> 00:36:14.625
because normally they don't have Omkar name.

00:36:14.917 --> 00:36:16.375
So I said, “Who gave you this name?”

00:36:16.667 --> 00:36:20.083
He said, “I went to a monastery.” And what happened?

00:36:20.375 --> 00:36:22.208
All his bones were broken.

00:36:22.500 --> 00:36:25.834
He said, “They beat me on my back.” Just imagine.

00:36:26.125 --> 00:36:28.166
How can that be?

00:36:28.458 --> 00:36:29.750
All his bones were broken.

00:36:30.125 --> 00:36:32.417
And it was impossible to give him realization, because

00:36:32.750 --> 00:36:34.417
physically it was impossible.

00:36:34.750 --> 00:36:37.625
But slowly and steadily he is now recovering.

00:36:37.875 --> 00:36:39.750
He's like a madman.

00:36:40.667 --> 00:36:43.333
How can you be cruel?

00:36:45.917 --> 00:36:48.999
So Tibetans, are they very realized souls, you think?

00:36:49.208 --> 00:36:52.583
What is there to learn from Tibetans?

00:36:57.250 --> 00:37:00.834
Anybody who is foreign need not be a learned

00:37:01.041 --> 00:37:02.500
personality.

00:37:03.000 --> 00:37:08.250
Whatever is written in the book need not be a scripture.

00:37:08.709 --> 00:37:12.458
You should understand that all these things have come up

00:37:12.959 --> 00:37:16.250
just after Buddha's death.

00:37:16.625 --> 00:37:19.291
It has happened with every religion, with every great

00:37:19.583 --> 00:37:22.667
personality came on this earth, it has happened.

00:37:22.999 --> 00:37:29.792
But it is in the old caves the saints who lived after Buddha

00:37:30.041 --> 00:37:32.583
have written that it is a spontaneous happening.

00:37:33.000 --> 00:37:35.542
But Buddha did not talk of God because He thought,

00:37:35.834 --> 00:37:37.375
“First talk of the Self.

00:37:37.667 --> 00:37:39.625
Because if you talk of God, people immediately start

00:37:39.917 --> 00:37:41.375
thinking they have become God.

00:37:41.750 --> 00:37:44.999
So better talk of Self; let them get their Self-realization.

00:37:45.250 --> 00:37:47.041
Unless and until they get Self-realization,

00:37:47.375 --> 00:37:49.000
how will they understand God?”

00:37:49.375 --> 00:37:51.500
So they are called, He is called as Anishwar, means

00:37:51.500 --> 00:37:54.458
He doesn't believe in God, an atheist: it's not so.

00:37:54.709 --> 00:37:56.792
He just deliberately did it because He thought,

00:37:57.083 --> 00:38:01.375
if you talk of something far-fetched then people live

00:38:01.709 --> 00:38:03.250
in an imaginary world.

00:38:03.625 --> 00:38:06.583
So what He wanted practically to have Self-realization

00:38:06.875 --> 00:38:09.999
first, and then the knowledge about God.

00:38:09.999 --> 00:38:13.041
Because for a blind person, no use telling him about

00:38:13.375 --> 00:38:15.834
the whole thing, before first tell him that

00:38:16.250 --> 00:38:19.458
“you must have your vision.”

00:38:25.041 --> 00:38:28.125
The other day we had one lady from Buddhist meditation,

00:38:28.500 --> 00:38:30.500
she couldn't get her realization, I'm sorry to say, though

00:38:30.917 --> 00:38:34.166
we can work it out gradually; but she couldn't get it.

00:38:34.500 --> 00:38:38.625
Because you see, Buddha resides within us, on this side

00:38:38.959 --> 00:38:40.250
here.

00:38:40.583 --> 00:38:43.208
And this is the portion gets very much swollen up when

00:38:43.542 --> 00:38:47.125
you do Buddhist meditation and we have to reduce it with

00:38:47.375 --> 00:38:52.291
certain mantras, otherwise you cannot reduce it.

00:38:52.750 --> 00:38:56.750
One has to work hard for such people – doesn't matter.

00:38:57.041 --> 00:38:58.959
Because you are all seekers it's your right to have it,

00:38:59.417 --> 00:39:02.333
and I am here to work for you.

00:39:04.250 --> 00:39:06.166
Any other question, please?

00:39:08.458 --> 00:39:10.458
Lady in audience comments on how people

00:39:11.041 --> 00:39:12.542
don’t want to know about the spirit.

00:39:12.792 --> 00:39:15.417
Yes, that's the problem in England.

00:39:22.125 --> 00:39:25.875
I know, I know. I know that's the problem today is that

00:39:26.166 --> 00:39:28.333
they don't want to know and they are very skeptical.

00:39:28.750 --> 00:39:30.333
But things are working out nicely now.

00:39:30.667 --> 00:39:34.208
You see, what it is after all, God is also anxious that

00:39:34.542 --> 00:39:35.625
people should get it.

00:39:36.083 --> 00:39:37.542
Now I'll tell you how it’s working out.

00:39:37.875 --> 00:39:42.250
Like the other day, I was not there but My husband saw

00:39:42.625 --> 00:39:47.125
a program about a comedian who said that he gets a cool

00:39:47.458 --> 00:39:49.917
breeze – you see, he was talking about his revelation.

00:39:50.291 --> 00:39:52.417
He said, “Suddenly I started getting cool breeze in my

00:39:52.834 --> 00:39:56.500
back and I don't know what it is,

00:39:56.875 --> 00:40:00.875
but I felt very relaxed and so many people feel relaxed

00:40:01.250 --> 00:40:03.917
when they sit together with me.”

00:40:04.625 --> 00:40:07.041
Now, he doesn't know anything, he's very vague about

00:40:07.041 --> 00:40:09.250
the cool breeze, but he, he felt it.

00:40:09.625 --> 00:40:11.125
That's a revelation he gives.

00:40:11.125 --> 00:40:13.959
Now just before that, a day, two days before, we were

00:40:14.417 --> 00:40:17.166
discussing amongst themselves and they said, “Mother,

00:40:17.417 --> 00:40:19.959
how many people you need to have that syndrome?”

00:40:20.166 --> 00:40:21.500
What is it called as?

00:40:22.458 --> 00:40:24.917
Hundred monkey syndrome. I hope you have heard about it,

00:40:25.291 --> 00:40:27.542
that when the hundred monkey learnt a trick,

00:40:27.875 --> 00:40:30.166
every monkey everywhere started doing that trick,

00:40:30.458 --> 00:40:31.417
sort of a thing.

00:40:32.041 --> 00:40:33.709
I said, “It will be very soon."

00:40:33.999 --> 00:40:35.999
And just imagine, this fellow started feeling this

00:40:36.250 --> 00:40:37.917
cool breeze on his back.

00:40:37.917 --> 00:40:40.458
Now he came on the television, and the television were

00:40:40.917 --> 00:40:43.250
very, very skeptical as you say – very, very.

00:40:43.667 --> 00:40:46.500
And I didn't bother much about it. I said,

00:40:46.834 --> 00:40:51.458
“The time will come by itself” – because we don’t take

00:40:51.834 --> 00:40:55.417
any money, and we cannot pay any money for any such things.

00:40:55.875 --> 00:40:59.500
Now when somebody met them and told them that this

00:40:59.875 --> 00:41:01.834
program has taken place, there's somebody who knows

00:41:02.166 --> 00:41:04.417
all about this thing, immediately they came to Me.

00:41:04.792 --> 00:41:06.166
And now they want Me to have a program.

00:41:06.583 --> 00:41:09.166
And once it starts like that, people will come round.

00:41:09.500 --> 00:41:11.792
The trouble is, you see, human beings have so much of a

00:41:12.166 --> 00:41:14.083
barrier of their ego also.

00:41:14.375 --> 00:41:16.166
They are very insensitive people.

00:41:16.458 --> 00:41:19.750
Moreover, say, a traditional country like say, Rome,

00:41:20.000 --> 00:41:23.500
Egypt, I find they are much more sensitive to divinity than

00:41:23.834 --> 00:41:25.166
to absurd things.

00:41:25.500 --> 00:41:27.750
You'll be surprised, in Rome now – we are sitting down

00:41:28.000 --> 00:41:30.291
here, so I can tell you – in Rome no guru has been

00:41:30.625 --> 00:41:32.500
successful. No guru has been successful.

00:41:32.792 --> 00:41:35.291
But when I went there, just seeing My photograph, just

00:41:35.542 --> 00:41:38.291
seeing My photograph the mayor was so amazed.

00:41:38.625 --> 00:41:40.750
He said “It's divinity” – just seeing My photograph.

00:41:41.166 --> 00:41:44.333
And he took it over, he gave us a hall free, he published it

00:41:44.667 --> 00:41:47.750
and he made so many posters, he put it all over.

00:41:48.125 --> 00:41:50.625
And it's working very well in Rome.

00:41:50.999 --> 00:41:52.500
But not in England. I have been here for ten years

00:41:52.959 --> 00:41:57.417
working hard, but English are rather hard people.

00:41:57.792 --> 00:41:59.250
Doesn't matter, it will work out.

00:41:59.709 --> 00:42:03.041
And then also in Egypt. Egypt is another place which are

00:42:03.291 --> 00:42:04.709
very traditional people.

00:42:05.083 --> 00:42:06.750
Another I have found is Greece.

00:42:07.125 --> 00:42:08.875
They are very traditional, and they – in tradition what

00:42:09.166 --> 00:42:12.166
happens, you start learning by making mistakes, you see.

00:42:12.583 --> 00:42:14.625
You believe in Rasputin, you believe in this and believe in

00:42:14.917 --> 00:42:18.500
that; and then you start understanding what is reality,

00:42:18.750 --> 00:42:19.709
how we’ll get it.

00:42:19.709 --> 00:42:20.834
And that’s how they come to it.

00:42:21.291 --> 00:42:23.208
But here just people read, read, read and they reach

00:42:23.625 --> 00:42:25.250
nowhere, they are so confused.

00:42:25.625 --> 00:42:27.041
I don't blame them for all this.

00:42:27.041 --> 00:42:30.250
But I must say that they must come to terms with reality

00:42:30.667 --> 00:42:33.834
and try to understand that you cannot purchase it,

00:42:34.291 --> 00:42:39.333
first of all, and you cannot work for it

00:42:39.999 --> 00:42:44.208
It is a spontaneous, living process of the living God.

00:42:44.625 --> 00:42:46.250
This is what we have to understand.

00:42:46.625 --> 00:42:49.291
And once we understand that it will work out, I'm sure.

00:42:49.625 --> 00:42:51.917
I understand that people are like that.

00:42:52.375 --> 00:42:55.041
And you'll be surprised, I've been working ten years in

00:42:55.375 --> 00:42:59.750
England and we don't have so many Sahaja yogis

00:43:00.000 --> 00:43:01.750
as we have in other, other countries.

00:43:02.000 --> 00:43:03.959
Even France is better, surprisingly.

00:43:04.291 --> 00:43:07.542
Much better off, France, and Switzerland is much better.

00:43:07.542 --> 00:43:10.375
But England is the one that is lacking very much, and I’m

00:43:10.750 --> 00:43:12.083
and I’m working very hard here.

00:43:12.542 --> 00:43:14.625
India of course, is thousand times more.

00:43:14.959 --> 00:43:16.500
So it's all right, it will come.

00:43:16.792 --> 00:43:18.917
English are that way very balanced – sometimes over-

00:43:19.208 --> 00:43:21.417
balanced, you see!

00:43:23.792 --> 00:43:25.000
One thing good about them, they know

00:43:25.375 --> 00:43:26.999
how to laugh at themselves.

00:43:27.291 --> 00:43:29.125
So it may work out.

00:43:32.834 --> 00:43:36.542
[Audience question repeated by a yogi:

00:43:43.291 --> 00:43:48.250
She says that You said that the gurus often do more harm

00:43:48.834 --> 00:43:52.291
than good. How do we know that You may not be doing

00:43:52.542 --> 00:43:53.625
more harm than good?]

00:43:53.999 --> 00:43:56.000
Yes, of course, may be, I may be doing, no doubt; you

00:43:56.375 --> 00:43:57.542
must keep that open.

00:43:57.917 --> 00:43:59.959
But you can talk to people who are …

00:44:00.250 --> 00:44:02.500
Always, when you go to a guru – actually I've seen when

00:44:02.917 --> 00:44:04.750
you come to Me, you ask Me questions,

00:44:05.166 --> 00:44:07.375
but when you go to these people you go headlong,

00:44:07.750 --> 00:44:08.959
absolutely headlong.

00:44:09.417 --> 00:44:11.500
I've known people who paid six thousand pounds to go to

00:44:11.792 --> 00:44:16.542
Switzerland and eat only potato, water of the potato that

00:44:16.792 --> 00:44:17.709
is boiled.

00:44:18.000 --> 00:44:20.583
And they lived there without asking a question.

00:44:20.917 --> 00:44:22.999
That is one of the signs that you are free.

00:44:23.333 --> 00:44:27.625
Secondly, you must know that what others have been,

00:44:28.083 --> 00:44:32.333
others have been to Me, what has happened to them.

00:44:32.709 --> 00:44:35.375
Thirdly, you should know, why should I harm you?

00:44:35.709 --> 00:44:37.041
What is My advantage?

00:44:37.458 --> 00:44:39.041
Because I don't take any money from you,

00:44:39.375 --> 00:44:40.208
nothing of the kind.

00:44:40.583 --> 00:44:42.417
By God's grace, I'm living very well in My life.

00:44:42.709 --> 00:44:45.333
Perhaps I'm very well-off in life, I don't need anything

00:44:45.667 --> 00:44:48.041
from anyone, so why should I do it?

00:44:48.458 --> 00:44:52.208
On another life where I am, I'm at a very high level,

00:44:52.583 --> 00:44:54.417
so, why should I come to you?

00:44:54.709 --> 00:44:59.166
For what? What am I going to gain out of you?

00:44:59.500 --> 00:45:02.291
So credibility must be established through the disciples.

00:45:02.625 --> 00:45:03.875
You never see the disciples.

00:45:04.250 --> 00:45:06.333
You just go headlong because you are mesmerized.

00:45:06.333 --> 00:45:07.792
You don't even think about it.

00:45:08.083 --> 00:45:09.792
You don't even ask questions. I asked them,

00:45:10.041 --> 00:45:10.917
“Why didn't you ask questions,

00:45:11.250 --> 00:45:12.917
why are you taking six thousand pounds?”

00:45:13.291 --> 00:45:16.083
“Oh,” they said, “Mother, we were walking under the blanket.”

00:45:16.458 --> 00:45:19.375
And the person who was the head of that organization in

00:45:19.792 --> 00:45:22.834
Scotland became epileptic, his daughter became

00:45:23.083 --> 00:45:25.999
epileptic, his wife became epileptic, and he was – he

00:45:26.291 --> 00:45:28.667
then, then he came to Me.

00:45:28.999 --> 00:45:31.667
Then he came to Me in that state and I took him,

00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:34.709
them in My house to cure them.

00:45:36.709 --> 00:45:38.875
So those people who have been to Me,

00:45:39.166 --> 00:45:41.917
like Dr. Warren has been: now he was a patient of high

00:45:42.250 --> 00:45:44.291
blood pressure, all kinds of things, he got cured – not

00:45:44.625 --> 00:45:45.917
only, he's cured many people.

00:45:46.291 --> 00:45:48.500
And there are so many here who have been helped.

00:45:48.875 --> 00:45:51.500
People who used to, were alcoholics, drug addicts, this,

00:45:51.834 --> 00:45:53.291
all of them have become all right.

00:45:53.750 --> 00:45:56.709
So you must see them and see how they are, and you

00:45:57.000 --> 00:45:58.959
can see how they talk, how they know.

00:45:59.333 --> 00:46:03.041
But in any other guru's place, they – it’s such a hierarchy

00:46:03.417 --> 00:46:05.125
you cannot even reach them.

00:46:05.542 --> 00:46:07.208
And somebody who talks is, remembers everything by

00:46:07.583 --> 00:46:10.417
heart and says something, there's nothing spontaneous,

00:46:10.750 --> 00:46:13.667
nothing; they don't know anything about it.

00:46:13.999 --> 00:46:15.959
So credibility must be established first of all.

00:46:16.333 --> 00:46:18.834
But that you don't do with anybody else, only with Me.

00:46:19.041 --> 00:46:24.583
That's a good sign for Me, that I give you freedom.

00:46:37.041 --> 00:46:40.166
She says that surely all paths lead to Rome.

00:46:40.709 --> 00:46:44.250
You were speaking about the Dalai Lama, and so what's wrong?

00:46:44.583 --> 00:46:48.291
No, but some lead to hell also. We must know.

00:46:48.750 --> 00:46:51.834
Every doesn't go to Rome, but can go to hell also.

00:46:52.166 --> 00:46:56.375
Of course, all paths lead to Rome if the person who takes

00:46:56.709 --> 00:47:00.834
you there is a right guide, is the right guide.

00:47:01.208 --> 00:47:04.999
You cannot go to hell and then, say, come back to Rome.

00:47:05.333 --> 00:47:07.041
You cannot.

00:47:07.375 --> 00:47:09.959
But the people who are right guides can do it.

00:47:10.250 --> 00:47:12.500
They don't take any money, they don't do.

00:47:12.875 --> 00:47:14.166
They give you realization.

00:47:14.542 --> 00:47:15.875
They make you something different.

00:47:16.250 --> 00:47:19.542
They make you righteous, virtuous and great people.

00:47:19.959 --> 00:47:23.291
It's a very different thing: are not those who just profess

00:47:23.625 --> 00:47:25.500
something, or say something.

00:47:25.875 --> 00:47:27.625
They do not accumulate wealth.

00:47:27.625 --> 00:47:28.875
You see, they are self-respecting people,

00:47:29.125 --> 00:47:30.125
they are not parasites.

00:47:30.458 --> 00:47:33.166
They don't live on your living.

00:47:34.375 --> 00:47:36.041
How much did Christ earn?

00:47:36.417 --> 00:47:38.542
You have such a great example of Christ.

00:47:38.917 --> 00:47:40.792
Why do you go to anybody else?

00:47:41.125 --> 00:47:43.041
Did He take any money?

00:47:43.417 --> 00:47:46.208
He was sold for thirty rupees.

00:47:49.125 --> 00:47:51.999
What Christ has said, “Thou shalt not have adulterous eyes."

00:47:52.375 --> 00:47:54.709
I would like to know what Christians are there, which

00:47:55.000 --> 00:47:59.208
Christians have those eyes which are not adulterous.

00:47:59.542 --> 00:48:01.458
Have you got innocent eyes?

00:48:01.917 --> 00:48:03.667
There’s no lust and greed in your eyes?

00:48:03.999 --> 00:48:05.500
Face yourself.

00:48:06.166 --> 00:48:09.166
Those who talk of these things have all those, much

00:48:09.500 --> 00:48:12.166
greater sins than what you have.

00:48:12.542 --> 00:48:14.417
How can they improve you?

00:48:14.792 --> 00:48:16.917
They are the ones who are living on others' property,

00:48:17.250 --> 00:48:18.250
others' money.

00:48:18.625 --> 00:48:21.125
Will you live on somebody else's property and earnings?

00:48:21.458 --> 00:48:23.625
They are making the children to get out of their houses,

00:48:23.917 --> 00:48:25.375
sell their houses, go on the streets.

00:48:25.750 --> 00:48:28.125
Will you do that? For anyone?

00:48:28.500 --> 00:48:30.333
Taking money from the poor, will you do that?

00:48:30.750 --> 00:48:34.250
You are so good! Must understand.

00:48:34.583 --> 00:48:37.625
Use your brains.

00:48:40.583 --> 00:48:42.208
But when you get realization,

00:48:42.625 --> 00:48:44.458
you develop those innocent eyes.

00:48:44.750 --> 00:48:45.999
The eyes are so powerful.

00:48:45.999 --> 00:48:47.834
Even looking at somebody with those eyes,

00:48:48.333 --> 00:48:51.125
you can give realization.

00:48:51.583 --> 00:48:52.667
You can cure them.

00:48:53.083 --> 00:48:56.542
Like the other day we had one – what was his name,

00:48:57.417 --> 00:48:59.166
the one who came to …?

00:48:59.667 --> 00:49:02.500
One journalist, you see, who came and who said that

00:49:02.959 --> 00:49:04.834
“It is said that You can cure people.”

00:49:05.125 --> 00:49:06.000
I said, “All right.”

00:49:06.375 --> 00:49:08.166
So he said, “There's one lady who's suffering from the

00:49:08.458 --> 00:49:12.375
disease of agoraphobia, and she doesn't want to come

00:49:12.667 --> 00:49:14.959
out of her house, so how will You cure her?”

00:49:15.250 --> 00:49:16.917
I said, “All right, if she cannot come, get Me her

00:49:17.250 --> 00:49:18.999
photograph; I can't go to her house” – sort of challenging

00:49:19.333 --> 00:49:22.959
Me. I said, “All right, bring her photograph to Me.”

00:49:23.291 --> 00:49:24.417
He brought a photograph to Me.

00:49:24.417 --> 00:49:25.999
I just looked at the photograph.

00:49:26.375 --> 00:49:28.458
“She's like this for ten years,” he said; and he said,

00:49:28.875 --> 00:49:30.625
“You must cure her.” I said, “All right, I'll try.

00:49:31.250 --> 00:49:33.041
It's very easy to cure this disease at least.”

00:49:34.667 --> 00:49:37.500
And I said, “You just leave her alone for eight days.”

00:49:37.834 --> 00:49:42.083
But he couldn't, you see, resist, so he went like a C.I.D.

00:49:42.458 --> 00:49:44.625
there to find out what was going on.

00:49:45.000 --> 00:49:47.000
And when he went to her house she was not there.

00:49:47.458 --> 00:49:49.375
She was out on the move with her husband,

00:49:49.750 --> 00:49:50.500
having a nice stroll.

00:49:50.917 --> 00:49:55.417
And he's now going to publish a very good article about it.

00:50:03.000 --> 00:50:04.959
Question: Do You see Yourself as a spiritual healer?

00:50:05.500 --> 00:50:07.917
No, not at all. Not a healer.

00:50:08.208 --> 00:50:09.166
I'm not a healer at all.

00:50:09.625 --> 00:50:12.333
I am a person who wants to give you Self-realization.

00:50:12.709 --> 00:50:14.041
It's not question of spiritual healing.

00:50:14.458 --> 00:50:16.500
Spiritual healing are also two types:

00:50:16.875 --> 00:50:20.000
one of them is of course the people who are realized souls.

00:50:20.375 --> 00:50:22.542
Like the other day we went – of course, we met somebody.

00:50:23.041 --> 00:50:28.000
(Where was that, a taxi fellow who came with us?)

00:50:28.375 --> 00:50:29.375
[Yogi: In Nottingham.]

00:50:29.875 --> 00:50:32.834
Aah. The taxi gentleman who came in the car thing,

00:50:33.125 --> 00:50:35.041
I knew he was a realized soul.

00:50:35.417 --> 00:50:36.500
So he just started talking to Me.

00:50:36.917 --> 00:50:38.417
He also felt that nearness.

00:50:38.792 --> 00:50:40.667
And I said, “Do your fingers tingle sometimes?"

00:50:40.959 --> 00:50:42.625
He said, “Yes, very much."

00:50:42.999 --> 00:50:44.041
I said, “Are you a healer?"

00:50:44.417 --> 00:50:45.542
“Yes,” he said, “I'm a healer.”

00:50:45.542 --> 00:50:46.834
He said, “How do you know all about it?"

00:50:47.208 --> 00:50:49.875
I said, “Do you feel very guilty?" “Yes.”

00:50:50.208 --> 00:50:51.250
“Oh,” I said, “I know that."

00:50:51.583 --> 00:50:52.291
He said, “How do you know?"

00:50:52.667 --> 00:50:53.999
I said, “I know somehow.

00:50:54.208 --> 00:50:55.458
But you want to know about it.”

00:50:55.834 --> 00:50:57.291
Because he was a realized soul.

00:50:57.542 --> 00:50:58.333
He was a realized soul.

00:50:58.709 --> 00:51:00.583
But there are healers who are not realized souls.

00:51:00.875 --> 00:51:02.583
They are the people who use spirits.

00:51:02.875 --> 00:51:04.208
They shake before you and shout and –

00:51:04.458 --> 00:51:08.166
that's very dangerous.

00:51:08.750 --> 00:51:10.375
A realized soul doesn't have to do anything.

00:51:10.875 --> 00:51:12.792
Only touches you, you’ll be all right.

00:51:13.083 --> 00:51:16.709
He doesn't have to shake and do all these tantrums.

00:51:17.333 --> 00:51:19.583
Because you are so naive, I must say,

00:51:19.959 --> 00:51:22.917
that's why there is such a problem. Very naive.

00:51:23.291 --> 00:51:25.542
In the West we have developed our tree very well,

00:51:25.959 --> 00:51:26.500
but not the roots.

00:51:27.083 --> 00:51:28.166
We don't know anything about the roots.

00:51:28.667 --> 00:51:32.709
I was amazed Myself, because there's no idea at all.

00:51:33.125 --> 00:51:35.917
Not in India – India people know this.

00:51:36.166 --> 00:51:37.041
They know this.

00:51:37.458 --> 00:51:39.333
Like we put dead in the church.

00:51:39.625 --> 00:51:41.208
In India nobody would put dead in the church –

00:51:41.500 --> 00:51:44.834
it's a, is a holy place, how do you put the dead there?

00:51:45.125 --> 00:51:46.208
But this is what it is.

00:51:46.667 --> 00:51:49.166
You are naive, I know, and despite that, that naivety,

00:51:49.542 --> 00:51:51.041
you are also very adamant.

00:51:51.041 --> 00:51:52.208
Though what to do now:

00:51:52.750 --> 00:51:54.375
it's a difficult question sometimes for Me.

00:51:54.750 --> 00:51:58.041
Doesn't matter. It works out. Yes?

00:51:59.250 --> 00:52:03.834
[Inaudible question.] What say?

00:52:07.583 --> 00:52:09.291
[Yogi repeats: Could You explain what You mean by this

00:52:09.709 --> 00:52:11.709
energy rising through the spine?

00:52:12.208 --> 00:52:14.667
And isn't it just really the same thing as a tingling up the

00:52:14.959 --> 00:52:17.375
spine, perhaps…(addressed to questioner:

00:52:17.667 --> 00:52:19.917
Do you mean of a more physical kind?)]

00:52:20.166 --> 00:52:24.041
[Questioner: A feeling of awe.]

00:52:24.500 --> 00:52:26.458
Yes. Feeling of …. Awe?

00:52:26.834 --> 00:52:29.291
[Yogi: Yes, he's relating the feeling that you might have

00:52:29.667 --> 00:52:32.375
up your spine to a feeling of awe, and perhaps saying it’s

00:52:32.375 --> 00:52:35.417
There is not, no – I have not known such a thing as that.  I

00:52:35.917 --> 00:52:36.834
don't know.

00:52:37.250 --> 00:52:38.667
That’s a – it doesn't happen like that.

00:52:39.083 --> 00:52:41.250
You see, when the Kundalini rises you don't feel anything,

00:52:41.625 --> 00:52:42.750
nothing of the kind.

00:52:43.041 --> 00:52:46.083
Only thing you feel at top of your head a cool breeze.

00:52:46.500 --> 00:52:49.250
All right? And in the hands you feel a kind of a cool

00:52:49.542 --> 00:52:50.709
breeze coming out.

00:52:51.125 --> 00:52:52.999
But in the beginning you might feel little heat,

00:52:53.375 --> 00:52:54.999
because if you have too much heat in the body,

00:52:55.375 --> 00:52:57.291
then you might feel a little heat coming out.

00:52:57.709 --> 00:53:00.750
Sometimes people who are very nervous type shake a

00:53:00.999 --> 00:53:02.166
little, that's all.

00:53:02.458 --> 00:53:04.417
But this thing I have never known, is some sort of a funny

00:53:04.709 --> 00:53:07.709
thing maybe coming from somewhere – I don't know.

00:53:08.000 --> 00:53:10.667
All kinds of  permutations and combinations I’ve seen

00:53:11.000 --> 00:53:12.000
happening to people.

00:53:12.000 --> 00:53:14.667
Like one gentleman, he sat on the ground with the feet

00:53:15.041 --> 00:53:16.750
with the feet towards Me – in India is not done.

00:53:17.041 --> 00:53:18.500
So people said that “How can you put your feet

00:53:18.875 --> 00:53:20.166
towards Mother? It is not done.”

00:53:20.625 --> 00:53:21.959
So he said, “No, my Kundalini's awakened

00:53:22.375 --> 00:53:24.458
and I'll jump like a frog.”

00:53:24.834 --> 00:53:25.583
I said, “Who told you?"

00:53:25.875 --> 00:53:28.000
He showed Me a book of his guru, written down that you

00:53:28.291 --> 00:53:29.834
jump like a frog. Can you imagine?

00:53:30.208 --> 00:53:34.000
I asked him, “Will you, are you going to become a frog now?"

00:53:34.333 --> 00:53:36.041
All kinds of permutations and combinations:

00:53:36.417 --> 00:53:39.583
you don't know how many things are there published

00:53:39.875 --> 00:53:41.625
all over the world.

00:53:44.875 --> 00:53:47.041
[Yogi: Right, he wants to know how is this awakening

00:53:47.375 --> 00:53:50.375
initiated – the awakening of the Kundalini.]

00:53:50.709 --> 00:53:53.333
It’s very simple as I told you, just like sprouting of the

00:53:53.667 --> 00:53:55.125
seed. That's My job.

00:53:55.667 --> 00:53:58.917
But then once I have done it, you have to do it also.

00:53:59.208 --> 00:54:01.583
All right? On that promise.

00:54:03.667 --> 00:54:05.750
[Question: You say that false gurus and teachers can lead

00:54:06.125 --> 00:54:09.375
maybe to hell. Can You define hell?]

00:54:09.792 --> 00:54:13.375
Now, at this good time, why do you want to know hell?

00:54:13.750 --> 00:54:16.999
You see, it is described very well if you read any one of

00:54:17.375 --> 00:54:18.583
these great poets.

00:54:19.000 --> 00:54:22.792
Specially I would say, read William Blake. All right?

00:54:23.125 --> 00:54:25.291
It's already described so much, why do you want?

00:54:25.792 --> 00:54:28.208
I want, I want you to enter into the Kingdom of God.

00:54:28.625 --> 00:54:32.166
Hell is, when I'm saying “to hell”: you might get epilepsy.

00:54:32.875 --> 00:54:36.125
Now I've seen people getting epilepsy, people getting

00:54:36.500 --> 00:54:39.208
lunatic, leaving their homes, running away, hitting

00:54:39.542 --> 00:54:44.250
everyone, killing each other, killing themselves, killing

00:54:44.583 --> 00:54:50.417
their parents, violent, they take to drugs, take to all kinds

00:54:50.709 --> 00:54:52.834
of things which are self-destructive.

00:54:53.125 --> 00:54:57.500
What I mean is “self-destructive”, in one word. All right?

00:55:03.250 --> 00:55:04.792
[Question: What about people who suffer from these

00:55:05.125 --> 00:55:06.125
things from birth?]

00:55:06.917 --> 00:55:10.041
Yes. All right. If they suffer from this, there is something

00:55:10.417 --> 00:55:11.709
else is responsible.

00:55:12.083 --> 00:55:13.208
But they do suffer, isn't it?

00:55:13.542 --> 00:55:16.041
But those who have not suffered and are normal and go

00:55:16.417 --> 00:55:18.625
to these gurus, pay money and get it, then at least you

00:55:18.917 --> 00:55:23.709
will hold these great gurus responsible, or not?

00:55:29.583 --> 00:55:31.583
What is it?

00:55:33.375 --> 00:55:34.959
[Question: Do you feel there are not any other gurus who

00:55:35.208 --> 00:55:37.208
Oh, many! There are many. But they are not in the

00:55:37.583 --> 00:55:40.375
market. There are many, many more.

00:55:40.792 --> 00:55:43.834
Many there ... beg pardon?

00:55:44.208 --> 00:55:46.375
[Yogi: Are there any who can be beneficial to you?]

00:55:46.709 --> 00:55:50.917
Beneficial to you? To anyone? Yes, they are.

00:55:51.291 --> 00:55:54.125
But just see now, in this crowd I'm talking to you, you're

00:55:54.500 --> 00:55:55.667
asking ten questions.

00:55:56.083 --> 00:55:57.625
They have no patience.

00:55:58.083 --> 00:55:59.750
They have no patience at all. I tell you, they are so

00:56:00.250 --> 00:56:04.375
impatient, all these gurus, that you have no idea.

00:56:04.792 --> 00:56:08.625
They just can't bear it. I asked one gentleman to go to

00:56:08.917 --> 00:56:11.750
America, with great coaxing and everything, because

00:56:12.125 --> 00:56:13.625
I had no time to go there.

00:56:13.959 --> 00:56:15.500
Within three days he ran away from there.

00:56:15.917 --> 00:56:18.417
He said, “I have no time for these stupid people."

00:56:18.750 --> 00:56:20.291
Just he cancelled it, you see.

00:56:20.667 --> 00:56:23.417
Because I'm a Mother, I have patience for you.

00:56:23.917 --> 00:56:26.000
They have no patience for you. What am I to do?

00:56:26.000 --> 00:56:28.208
They are telling Me, “After twelve years we'll come and

00:56:28.542 --> 00:56:30.667
help you, Mother.” They know Me very well.

00:56:31.000 --> 00:56:32.208
They are so many, so many.

00:56:32.625 --> 00:56:34.875
They have met some, but they don't want to talk to people

00:56:35.250 --> 00:56:37.999
who are – they think they are stupid.

00:56:38.291 --> 00:56:38.999
What to do, now?

00:56:39.542 --> 00:56:41.333
They think all seekers are stupid people.

00:56:41.750 --> 00:56:44.041
What am I to do? They have no patience.

00:56:44.375 --> 00:56:48.000
You have to have a Mother to have patience, isn't it?

00:56:52.333 --> 00:56:54.583
Now. There's no end to it, my child.

00:56:54.959 --> 00:56:56.750
These questions have no meaning.

00:56:57.083 --> 00:56:59.542
By asking questions you are not going to get realization,

00:56:59.917 --> 00:57:01.125
I must tell you.

00:57:01.625 --> 00:57:03.875
I cannot guarantee it. I cannot guarantee it.

00:57:04.375 --> 00:57:06.667
If you get it, it's your luck.

00:57:06.999 --> 00:57:09.917
If you don't get it, it's your luck. So be careful.

00:57:10.333 --> 00:57:13.333
There's no need to discuss, argue; by argument you are

00:57:13.667 --> 00:57:16.041
not going to get it. Listen to Me.

00:57:16.500 --> 00:57:18.125
What am I going to gain out of you?

00:57:18.542 --> 00:57:20.792
This is the first place where we have so many questions.

00:57:21.208 --> 00:57:24.375
Must be some Romans are around here, I think, reborn.

00:57:24.709 --> 00:57:27.291
Otherwise I can't explain. I mean, nobody asked so many

00:57:27.625 --> 00:57:29.834
questions as you have asked Me which has no meaning.

00:57:30.208 --> 00:57:32.792
And supporting the, these fake gurus who have taken

00:57:33.125 --> 00:57:35.999
money from you, have disturbed so many people;

00:57:36.250 --> 00:57:39.125
supporting satanic forces.

00:57:39.542 --> 00:57:41.917
Something surprising, isn't it?

00:57:42.208 --> 00:57:43.542
All right, doesn't matter.

00:57:43.917 --> 00:57:47.250
Now, I have already told that I'm – now, that's all.

00:57:47.250 --> 00:57:48.792
If you want Me to come back to Bath,

00:57:49.083 --> 00:57:51.250
please, no more questions now.

00:57:51.875 --> 00:57:53.417
But we'll see how many get realization here.

00:57:53.750 --> 00:57:55.667
That's the main point.

00:57:56.917 --> 00:57:58.250
Main point is not …

00:57:59.208 --> 00:58:02.709
You are going to be judged by your Kundalini – let's see.

00:58:03.083 --> 00:58:05.917
Before you judge Me, she's going to judge you.

00:58:06.250 --> 00:58:08.041
So let's see how many of you get realization.

00:58:08.375 --> 00:58:09.625
I cannot promise you.

00:58:10.000 --> 00:58:12.709
That's the main thing, I must tell you.

00:58:13.542 --> 00:58:15.959
All right. Let's see how it works out.

00:58:16.750 --> 00:58:18.542
Now whatever I have said, forget it.

00:58:19.250 --> 00:58:22.458
Let's have a pleasant relationship.

00:58:22.834 --> 00:58:25.583
That is, you are not to feel any guilty about anything,

00:58:25.875 --> 00:58:26.709
whatever I have said.

00:58:27.250 --> 00:58:28.583
You might have been to guru, you might have done

00:58:28.959 --> 00:58:31.250
anything that’s supposed to be wrong – all right.

00:58:31.625 --> 00:58:35.208
Just forget it. Just now you sit in the present.

00:58:35.583 --> 00:58:39.583
You have to be in the present to get your realization –

00:58:39.999 --> 00:58:41.250
that's the most important thing.

00:58:41.250 --> 00:58:43.500
You are born on this earth to be that,

00:58:43.917 --> 00:58:45.792
you are a human being to be that.

00:58:46.208 --> 00:58:48.250
You are not here just to waste your life.

00:58:48.667 --> 00:58:50.291
And that's what I have to tell you as a Mother,

00:58:50.792 --> 00:58:54.083
that you have to be humble about it.

00:58:54.458 --> 00:58:58.166
It's a very different realm you are in.

00:58:58.792 --> 00:59:01.667
It is nothing is selling here, it's not a shop.

00:59:02.083 --> 00:59:03.709
And here, it's a temple.

00:59:04.166 --> 00:59:06.917
And in a temple you have to be humble, and you have to

00:59:07.250 --> 00:59:10.166
get your realization: that should be your determination.

00:59:10.583 --> 00:59:13.041
But how many will get, that I cannot say.

00:59:13.709 --> 00:59:17.291
I'm sorry, but it's not a thing that I can promise all of you.

00:59:17.667 --> 00:59:20.625
But if it works out on some, I’ll be very satisfied.

00:59:20.999 --> 00:59:22.458
That's My job is.

00:59:22.875 --> 00:59:25.458
Now let's have very simple things, without asking any

00:59:25.792 --> 00:59:27.000
more questions.

00:59:27.458 --> 00:59:30.333
Now there's no need to be disturbed about it.

00:59:30.750 --> 00:59:32.667
If you have not asked one question, nothing goes wrong

00:59:33.041 --> 00:59:35.000
with you or with audience.

00:59:35.375 --> 00:59:37.375
I tell you, even if you ask hundred questions it's not going

00:59:37.709 --> 00:59:39.375
to make any difference.

00:59:39.792 --> 00:59:42.375
I must say, so far nobody has asked anything

00:59:42.709 --> 00:59:45.959
that is intelligent, and I think you'd better now give up

00:59:46.333 --> 00:59:47.542
asking questions.

00:59:48.000 --> 00:59:50.166
I’m bit too intelligent for that.

00:59:50.166 --> 00:59:54.417
Now, let's have it the way it has to work out.

00:59:54.834 --> 00:59:56.999
Let's have it the way it has to work out.

00:59:57.375 --> 01:00:01.542
If you are seekers and if you are in the present,

01:00:01.999 --> 01:00:03.333
I'm sure you will get it.

01:00:03.750 --> 01:00:05.999
Now forget the past. Forget the past.

01:00:06.417 --> 01:00:09.000
One more thing I have to request, as I requested

01:00:09.333 --> 01:00:12.959
yesterday, that you are not to feel guilty about anything,

01:00:13.250 --> 01:00:14.999
because guilt comes from the past.

01:00:14.999 --> 01:00:17.999
So forget the past and you have to assert

01:00:18.333 --> 01:00:19.291
that you are not guilty.

01:00:19.875 --> 01:00:21.834
There are many people who are good, and they'll get it.

01:00:22.375 --> 01:00:26.000
So you have to assert that “I'm not guilty."

01:00:26.458 --> 01:00:29.166
Now, you have to call Me as Shri Mataji when you

01:00:29.542 --> 01:00:30.875
address, which is difficult.

01:00:31.291 --> 01:00:33.417
You can call Me Mother, to make it simpler – whichever

01:00:33.750 --> 01:00:34.834
way you like.

01:00:35.375 --> 01:00:37.834
So you have to say “Mother, I'm not guilty,” just before

01:00:38.250 --> 01:00:40.166
starting this process.

01:00:40.667 --> 01:00:42.959
Now, we have to humble down in our hearts, because we

01:00:43.375 --> 01:00:45.667
want to enter into the Kingdom of God.

01:00:46.041 --> 01:00:49.750
But the one who is trying to do it, if you are all the time

01:00:50.041 --> 01:00:52.583
attacking that person, how will you go?

01:00:52.917 --> 01:00:53.875
How will you enter in?

01:00:54.417 --> 01:00:55.959
Just look at that. What is our attitude?

01:00:56.458 --> 01:01:00.500
Is it proper? It's not being fair, not just.

01:01:02.166 --> 01:01:06.583
All right. So we take out our shoes just to take help

01:01:06.959 --> 01:01:07.792
from the Mother Earth.

01:01:08.458 --> 01:01:10.709
One of the very important elements is the Mother Earth.

01:01:11.125 --> 01:01:13.959
And this Kundalini is based in the sacrum bone, and the

01:01:14.250 --> 01:01:17.291
lower chakras are made from the element of Mother Earth.

01:01:17.792 --> 01:01:20.542
So just take out your shoes, very easily, to touch the

01:01:20.917 --> 01:01:22.500
Mother Earth with your feet.

01:01:22.917 --> 01:01:25.291
This Mother Earth is very important.

01:01:27.208 --> 01:01:29.625
[Yogi: Anyone who doesn't want the experience, please,

01:01:30.041 --> 01:01:31.959
you should leave now, anyone who doesn’t want …]

01:01:32.333 --> 01:01:34.291
Leave. Don't disturb others. You be kind.

01:01:34.709 --> 01:01:36.999
You have to be civil. You have to be civil people.

01:01:37.458 --> 01:01:38.875
Don't disturb others.

01:01:39.166 --> 01:01:40.709
If you don't want to have, well and good.

01:01:41.166 --> 01:01:43.792
It's all right; you can go.

01:01:53.000 --> 01:01:55.750
Those who were yesterday in Bristol know

01:01:56.166 --> 01:01:58.417
how much I have worked hard on so many people

01:01:58.959 --> 01:02:01.250
for hours together to give them realization.

01:02:01.750 --> 01:02:04.583
And it's a thankless job. I tell you, it's a thankless job;

01:02:04.959 --> 01:02:06.875
because unless and until you establish yourself, it's such

01:02:07.166 --> 01:02:10.291
a waste, I feel, it’s a tremendous waste.

01:02:10.834 --> 01:02:13.542
Is just good for nothing, because you give them

01:02:13.875 --> 01:02:15.667
realization, they do not establish themselves

01:02:16.041 --> 01:02:18.959
and it's just such a waste.

01:02:19.875 --> 01:02:22.917
Now, age does not matter, race does not matter,

01:02:23.250 --> 01:02:24.750
community does not matter.

01:02:25.083 --> 01:02:29.333
As long as you are a human being, it works out –

01:02:29.750 --> 01:02:31.375
is as simple as that.

01:02:31.792 --> 01:02:35.125
So now you just have to put your hands straight on your

01:02:35.417 --> 01:02:39.999
lap, without feeling any discomfort while you are sitting.

01:02:40.333 --> 01:02:43.000
That's important, because I do not want that your,

01:02:43.500 --> 01:02:47.375
you should feel uncomfortable, and by that you start

01:02:47.709 --> 01:02:48.959
moving about.

01:02:49.375 --> 01:02:51.125
Now, you have to take out your shoes, please, because

01:02:51.500 --> 01:02:53.333
as it is Tibetan problems are there.

01:02:53.750 --> 01:02:55.542
If you want to have realization, take out your shoes,

01:02:55.875 --> 01:02:59.417
all right? Yes, just take them out. It's better.

01:02:59.792 --> 01:03:02.542
Socks, yes. Will be better because I want to work on you,

01:03:02.834 --> 01:03:04.458
definitely you are a seeker, all right?

01:03:04.875 --> 01:03:08.250
Put your hands like this. Yes.

01:03:09.834 --> 01:03:10.750
Hmm. Starting. Now.

01:03:16.000 --> 01:03:19.417
Despite everything, it's good. It's not so bad.

01:03:21.125 --> 01:03:24.000
Now, this left hand, as I told you, represents the left side,

01:03:24.375 --> 01:03:27.750
the emotional side; and the right side is the hand that

01:03:28.083 --> 01:03:30.000
represents the action.

01:03:30.417 --> 01:03:33.917
Now this is the desire that we have, the desire.

01:03:34.375 --> 01:03:37.834
So to put the desire hand on the left-hand side like this,

01:03:38.166 --> 01:03:42.999
straight all the time, when we have this process of giving

01:03:43.291 --> 01:03:45.583
relaxation to your chakras.

01:03:46.000 --> 01:03:49.417
Because some of the chakras are in augmented state and

01:03:49.834 --> 01:03:50.917
they are to be relaxed.

01:03:51.333 --> 01:03:53.917
You can do it yourself, and how you will do it I'll just tell you.

01:03:54.542 --> 01:03:56.208
There are, on the left-hand side

01:03:56.709 --> 01:03:58.041
we'll be touching those centers.

01:03:58.500 --> 01:04:01.583
Now one is in the heart where resides the spirit.

01:04:02.000 --> 01:04:04.917
Then one is in the upper part of the abdomen.

01:04:05.333 --> 01:04:08.875
And then another one in the lower part of the abdomen –

01:04:09.125 --> 01:04:11.375
all of them are on the left-hand side.

01:04:11.875 --> 01:04:14.041
Now, then one is here.

01:04:14.709 --> 01:04:17.208
This is the one you catch when you feel guilty.

01:04:17.583 --> 01:04:22.208
Like this, here, on the left-hand side of your neck.

01:04:22.583 --> 01:04:26.083
And then another one is here, and maybe here we may

01:04:26.417 --> 01:04:27.458
have to ask.

01:04:27.999 --> 01:04:30.750
And then you come up here on the fontanel bone area,

01:04:31.125 --> 01:04:34.291
where I'll ask you to put the palm on top of your fontanel

01:04:34.583 --> 01:04:35.917
bone area.

01:04:36.291 --> 01:04:38.208
Just now it's hot, but it will be all right. Let's do it.

01:04:38.959 --> 01:04:40.083
Now, it's very simple.

01:04:40.583 --> 01:04:42.667
You have to keep your eyes shut throughout, because

01:04:43.000 --> 01:04:44.625
there's no mesmerism, nothing like that.

01:04:45.125 --> 01:04:46.458
It has to happen within yourself.

01:04:46.834 --> 01:04:48.709
The attention is sucked in, and it's better to keep your

01:04:49.000 --> 01:04:51.333
eyes shut, because if your eyes are open the Kundalini

01:04:51.667 --> 01:04:52.875
may not rise.

01:04:53.291 --> 01:04:55.625
And it doesn't trouble you, it doesn't give you any problem

01:04:56.083 --> 01:04:59.375
– nothing of the kind; and you feel extremely relaxed,

01:05:00.000 --> 01:05:01.750
and you feel fine.

01:05:02.083 --> 01:05:05.041
All right. So now we close our eyes.

01:05:06.542 --> 01:05:10.667
First of all, please do not feel guilty for anything, even for

01:05:11.000 --> 01:05:14.041
asking questions or anything, don't feel guilty.

01:05:14.417 --> 01:05:17.250
Whatever I have said, just forget it.

01:05:17.625 --> 01:05:19.000
Be kind to yourself.

01:05:19.458 --> 01:05:22.208
Be very kind to yourself.

01:05:22.583 --> 01:05:24.917
And you have to respect yourself.

01:05:28.375 --> 01:05:32.250
Now, at this stage put your right hand on your heart,

01:05:32.583 --> 01:05:34.000
on the left-hand side.

01:05:34.542 --> 01:05:35.959
Left-hand side is the heart,

01:05:36.458 --> 01:05:39.291
so put your right hand on the heart.

01:05:39.792 --> 01:05:45.125
Now keep your eyes shut, and try to look within your

01:05:45.500 --> 01:05:48.709
heart, in the sense, put your attention to your heart and

01:05:49.083 --> 01:05:53.208
say – you have to ask now, Me, a real question which is

01:05:53.500 --> 01:05:55.125
the intelligent question.

01:05:55.542 --> 01:06:00.333
Ask a question, “Mother, am I the spirit?"

01:06:00.625 --> 01:06:06.583
Ask this question three times, “Mother, am I the spirit?"

01:06:06.959 --> 01:06:11.917
Ask this question three times, “Mother, am I the spirit?"

01:06:19.834 --> 01:06:23.458
(Left is too much, it’s left … Hm.)

01:06:31.500 --> 01:06:36.250
Now, raise this hand – I mean, lower this hand on the

01:06:36.583 --> 01:06:41.500
abdomen, on the upper part on the left-hand side.

01:06:42.000 --> 01:06:46.792
Lower this hand on the left-hand side, on the upper part of

01:06:47.000 --> 01:06:48.500
your stomach.

01:06:49.083 --> 01:06:54.041
Here is another center, the center of the Primordial Master.

01:06:55.041 --> 01:06:58.792
As you become, you become the spirit, you become the

01:06:59.083 --> 01:07:01.333
master, you become the guru.

01:07:01.999 --> 01:07:05.208
So now logically you have to ask another question,

01:07:05.625 --> 01:07:07.917
“Mother, am I my own master?”

01:07:08.250 --> 01:07:11.709
Ask a question, “Mother, am I my own master?”

01:07:12.000 --> 01:07:13.999
Ask the question three times.

01:07:14.417 --> 01:07:16.625
That's a sensible question.

01:07:16.999 --> 01:07:19.625
You are your own master, you don’t need any master

01:07:19.999 --> 01:07:20.959
whatsoever.

01:07:21.375 --> 01:07:25.834
I'm not your master, I'm just your Mother, that's all.

01:07:40.417 --> 01:07:43.542
Now. After asking this question you lower your hand

01:07:44.125 --> 01:07:46.834
again, on the lower part of your abdomen.

01:07:47.125 --> 01:07:49.125
And this is a very important center which is called as

01:07:49.625 --> 01:07:53.500
Swadisthan, which looks after the aortic plexus in our being.

01:07:54.999 --> 01:08:03.041
Now, press the fingers in and say at this point – because

01:08:03.709 --> 01:08:09.083
at this point, I must confess, I cannot cross your freedom.

01:08:09.458 --> 01:08:14.000
You are free to choose. If you want to have the true

01:08:14.417 --> 01:08:18.750
knowledge, you have to ask for it, I cannot force on you.

01:08:19.208 --> 01:08:21.500
So you have to say, “Mother, please give me true

01:08:21.875 --> 01:08:25.000
knowledge, give me pure knowledge. I want pure

01:08:25.375 --> 01:08:29.834
knowledge, the technique of pure knowledge” which is the

01:08:30.208 --> 01:08:35.999
another meaning of the word “yoga.”

01:08:37.750 --> 01:08:40.500
You have to say this six times because there are six

01:08:40.875 --> 01:08:43.250
petals to this center.

01:08:43.792 --> 01:08:48.333
There are six also plexuses, sub-plexuses to the aortic plexus.

01:08:54.750 --> 01:08:58.333
(Terrible! Left Swadisthan.)

01:09:02.834 --> 01:09:05.208
Hm – now.

01:09:25.250 --> 01:09:26.417
Again you are feeling guilty.

01:09:26.917 --> 01:09:28.000
Please don't feel guilty.

01:09:28.500 --> 01:09:29.875
Please don't feel guilty.

01:09:30.333 --> 01:09:31.500
Don't feel guilty for anything.

01:09:31.917 --> 01:09:35.917
You have done nothing wrong. (Ah, now better.)

01:09:37.625 --> 01:09:41.917
Now raise this hand again to the upper part of your

01:09:42.250 --> 01:09:48.000
stomach, where the center of the Primordial Master is.

01:09:48.417 --> 01:09:54.417
As you have asked for the technique, I will tell you, you

01:09:54.917 --> 01:09:58.208
have to at this center assert, to say,

01:09:58.208 --> 01:10:04.917
“I am my own master.” Just say that.

01:10:07.250 --> 01:10:09.500
You have to say ten times with full confidence,

01:10:10.083 --> 01:10:13.083
say, “Mother, I am my own master.”

01:10:13.500 --> 01:10:16.709
Because there are ten sub-plexuses, like ten valencies,

01:10:17.083 --> 01:10:19.041
we have these ten plexuses.

01:10:28.792 --> 01:10:31.917
Aah! Forget your masters.

01:10:34.250 --> 01:10:35.333
And forget all the slavery.

01:10:35.999 --> 01:10:45.583
Hah! All right. (All right. Good.) Ten times.

01:10:48.625 --> 01:10:51.792
All right. Good. Ten times.

01:11:00.750 --> 01:11:09.583
Now, raise this right hand to your heart, again to your

01:11:10.041 --> 01:11:14.166
heart. Here resides your spirit.

01:11:14.667 --> 01:11:17.542
Again in the technique, you assert –

01:11:17.959 --> 01:11:21.166
this is the mantra you have to say at this point,

01:11:22.250 --> 01:11:25.999
“Mother, I am the spirit."

01:11:26.291 --> 01:11:32.709
In all humility, in all your glory you accept, assume.

01:11:33.125 --> 01:11:37.291
“Mother, I am the spirit."

01:11:55.000 --> 01:11:57.792
(It’s good, very good.)

01:12:01.083 --> 01:12:04.792
You have to say this twelve times.

01:12:05.458 --> 01:12:06.999
But don't feel guilty.

01:12:07.458 --> 01:12:13.291
Now I have to tell you that God is the ocean of love.

01:12:13.834 --> 01:12:17.333
He's the ocean of compassion.

01:12:18.125 --> 01:12:22.709
But best of all, He is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:12:23.166 --> 01:12:26.375
So please don't feel guilty, because what sin can you

01:12:26.792 --> 01:12:30.834
commit that He cannot forgive?

01:12:31.250 --> 01:12:33.917
We are challenging His power of forgiveness

01:12:34.291 --> 01:12:35.250
when we feel guilty.

01:12:35.750 --> 01:12:38.375
Please don't feel guilty.

01:12:38.917 --> 01:12:45.458
Without feeling guilty, say “Mother, I am the spirit.”

01:12:46.375 --> 01:12:51.250
(Come down. All right. Ah, it’s better.)

01:12:58.125 --> 01:13:03.999
Twelve times, because there are twelve petals.

01:13:05.667 --> 01:13:09.041
(Left Nabhi. It’s more on the left, it’s all right.

01:13:09.458 --> 01:13:16.667
There’s nothing on the right. Ah!

01:13:23.834 --> 01:13:31.792
Better. But left Nabhi is too much.

01:13:34.542 --> 01:13:35.542
It moves from here.)

01:13:44.000 --> 01:13:51.375
Now, move this hand upward and put it, the right hand –

01:13:52.291 --> 01:13:54.000
you have to move the right hand, left hand towards Me –

01:13:55.542 --> 01:13:58.000
put it on the left-hand side of your neck.

01:13:58.667 --> 01:14:01.667
At the base, touching almost the left side of your spinal

01:14:02.125 --> 01:14:05.917
cord and pressing it a little with it.

01:14:06.417 --> 01:14:09.875
At this point, from the front – you have to do it, take the

01:14:10.291 --> 01:14:13.583
hand from the front, not from the back but from the front

01:14:13.959 --> 01:14:18.333
side – hold it tight.

01:14:18.834 --> 01:14:24.041
Here now you have to say, with full confidence, with all

01:14:24.667 --> 01:14:31.041
love and understanding about yourself,

01:14:31.500 --> 01:14:34.375
“Mother, I am not guilty.”

01:14:34.917 --> 01:14:37.208
Please say that, sixteen times.

01:14:37.709 --> 01:14:40.458
And if you are too much of it, you'd better say it hundred-

01:14:40.917 --> 01:14:44.959
and-eight times to punish yourself,

01:14:44.959 --> 01:14:49.917
if you are too indulgent in that kind of a thing!

01:15:02.709 --> 01:15:09.291
(It’s good. It’s rising up to the Agnya. Ah!)

01:15:31.333 --> 01:15:36.166
Now raise this hand on top, on top of your forehead

01:15:36.542 --> 01:15:38.000
across.

01:15:38.583 --> 01:15:40.875
And hold it, your forehead.

01:15:41.250 --> 01:15:44.166
At this point  – you know, as I told you, is the center of

01:15:44.542 --> 01:15:49.834
Christ – you have to forgive everyone.

01:15:50.250 --> 01:15:52.250
Some people might say, “It's very difficult, Mother, how

01:15:52.500 --> 01:15:53.709
can we forgive?”

01:15:54.000 --> 01:15:57.333
But it's a myth that you do not forgive anyone or you

01:15:57.667 --> 01:16:01.792
forgive anyone, because when you do not forgive,

01:16:02.125 --> 01:16:04.375
you suffer, not the other.

01:16:04.834 --> 01:16:08.792
So please say, “Mother, I forgive everyone.”

